The central continent is located within The 2nd Realm.
Inhabitants It contains species such as;
Minikin Demi-Slugs Silkvine States In addition, it is and has been home to the countries of Snixia, Morelland, the Empire of the Petrified Child, and the Sarvaran Civilisation.

Phantasmarrhoea is an illness caused by prolonged or sudden exposure to Alucinarium.
Symptoms Symptoms of Phantasmarrhoea include;
Alucinarium crystals growing on skin Irritability / Violence Psychosis Hallucinations Essential Shift Notable Examples Kempton Moss Kempton Moss underwent partial Phantasmarrhoea and sudden Essential Shift after coming into contact with the Fortuitary Gland of Florifera, his late wife, due to his murder of her.
